Program: Outlook
Title: 07/02/2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00nb3hg
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 8 Feb 2012
Matthew Bannister talks to Kimberley Motley, the only western lawyer practising in the Afghan court system whose advocacy skills are in increasing demand by Afghans. Also in the programme the five-foot-tall woman from Manipur who's a world champion boxer. And we speak to the Indonesian women living forty kilometres apart in Sweden who've just discovered they're twin sisters. Show less